{"tid":1965694,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同一日比ex個老母同鐘意嘅人話我一腳踏兩船","createTime":"2020-04-09T15:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T20:29:31.000Z","uid":355628,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fc01e9e4fb96aa4048030642986e7f47d9706e32","tid":1965694,"uid":355628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T15:40:51.000Z","msg":"我都想知自已做錯咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要唔知邊個放風岀嚟 <br />\n<br />\n我鐘意嗰個人仲要為咗呢件事喊到好慘 <br />\n佢個frd仲要特登打段嘢黎屌鳩我 <br />\n我真係由頭到尾黑人問號 <br />\n然後因為佢喊 所有人企囇喺佢個邊<br />\n係咪人越大 就要學習接受呢啲冤屈<br />\n係咪喊就代表真理 <br />\n係咪邊個傷心啲 就表示佢一定最慘 最大受害人"},{"pid":"0f41f4194fb13b787c64f0c64ea831183a096b74","tid":1965694,"uid":355628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T15:46:11.000Z","msg":"真係好無奈"},{"pid":"fb03ad2dea28ef0b45c201c04661c5f64c27ea92","tid":1965694,"uid":217385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T15:48:50.000Z","msg":"咩事？講多啲？"},{"pid":"6eaa8e05395a22c448961b791c27dbb796ba3492","tid":1965694,"uid":355628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T15:49:03.000Z","msg":"冇左段感情好似得佢一個會唔開心咁<br />\n有時唔喺人地面前表現出黎 唔等於冇事"},{"pid":"73e2ed3882e4a1df4af4f725cc29f0eca2f2ff37","tid":1965694,"uid":199902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T15:52:08.000Z","msg":"即係樓主嘅兩條船就係ex個老母同鍾意嘅人<br />\n樓主識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1645acd1324075f3778ed59a6ef03e0466a2d062","tid":1965694,"uid":355628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb03ad2dea28ef0b45c201c04661c5f64c27ea92","tid":1965694,"uid":217385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T15:48:50.000Z","msg":"咩事？講多啲？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T16:03:46.000Z","msg":"如題 真係覺得好心有不甘 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8154aaab6e9310a133a817f75e9b9b0fe9733931","tid":1965694,"uid":132470,"like":1,"dislike":